Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:38.88,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}Corrida Colosseum!\NThe Great Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.09,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.22,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Was that a devil fruit ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.53,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Probably, but what type of ability was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:08.28,Main,Fujitora,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:11.46,Main,Fujitora,0,0,0,,You can send the request for compensation to this address.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.05,Main,Clerk,0,0,0,,Uh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.75,Main,Clerk,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.60,Main,Clerk,0,0,0,,Sir, are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.31,Main,Fujitora,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're really strong, old guy!  Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:30.72,Main,Fujitora,0,0,0,,It would seem...\Nthat it'd be better for the both of us if I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.09,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Hey!  Why don't you watch where you're going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.36,Main,Fujitora,0,0,0,,I-I'm very sorry.  Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:44.44,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Better for the both of us?\NIs he like, some really infamous guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:48.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Whoever he is, he's definitely trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.16,Main,Man,0,0,0,,My bag's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.58,Main,Man,0,0,0,,And my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.45,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Where'd my wallet go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:56.38,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,Damn it!  My jacket's been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.28,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Even though it's midday,\Nthey still managed to sneak in through the dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.09,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Did the old guy pickpocket everyone, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.46,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,One of them is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.92,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.23,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,One of my swords is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.45,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Shuusui was right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:14.03,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,What?!  The treasure of the Wano Country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.00,Main,OH GOD KILL IT WITH FIRE,0,0,0,,It seems everyone's been had.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.42,Main,OH GOD KILL IT WITH FIRE,0,0,0,,The fairies stole them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:23.21,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!\NIs it some sort of criminal organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:27.31,Main,OH GOD KILL IT WITH FIRE,0,0,0,,Fairies are fairies.\NYou just have to laugh and accept what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:33.14,Main,OH GOD KILL IT WITH FIRE,0,0,0,,The fairies cannot be seen, but they have been the guardians of Dressrosa for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:37.32,Main,OH GOD KILL IT WITH FIRE,0,0,0,,We must turn a blind eye to whatever they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.56,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Guess there's nothing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.54,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.76,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Indeed!\NThat is a national treasure of the Wano Country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.75,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What?!  It's my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.49,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,It does not belong to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:54.15,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Sooner or later I will fight you for the blade and return it to its rightful home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.98,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Suits me fine!  I'll just take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.11,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Your greed was your downfall, fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.60,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You're not getting away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey Zoro, Where are you going!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.90,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:12.54,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We don't have time to let you wander off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.16,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.98,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Have you found the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.65,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,I will not let you run off\Nwith one of the Wano Country's treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let go of me!  I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.92,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I've got a great idea. { edit: I just realized something. }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:42.00,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I've come to realize that, in this group,\NI have to take the lead or nothing will get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.40,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me, the bro-meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.47,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You're one of Doflamingo's men, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.12,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to scare us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:06:01.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We asked you a question, mister.  Better spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.20,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,I-I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:10.72,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember chasing the samurai, but I have no idea how he was captured or where he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:14.54,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,And I've never heard of this Smile-thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.66,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Not even the letter S in Smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:21.68,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!\NAnd that goes for this factory of yours too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.76,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.41,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Well, this ain't good.\NEven his own men don't know, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.56,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Then tell us where we can find someone who gives you orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.41,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This guy might just be too low in their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.24,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,I have no idea where anybody is today.\NEveryone's too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.75,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Even I've been called to the colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.00,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:47.15,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,People from all over the country\Nare heading to the colosseum today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:52.33,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,The Corrida Colosseum.\NIf you wanna find the higher-ups, go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.00,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Today's a special event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:58.80,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,The Family's commanders are probably gonna be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:04.07,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,I dunno the details,\Nbut the young master's prepared a spectacular prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.65,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it when I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.88,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,It's something anyone would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,that ultra-delicious meat\Nthat Mingo was talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.57,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He only said that it was something you'd want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.16,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(420,0)}Dressrosa's Corrida Colosseum
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.10,Main,Child,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.16,Main,Child,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's him!  The Thunder Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:30.26,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ladies, gentlemen and toys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.64,Main,Child,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.33,Main,Child,0,0,0,,We wanna see too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.30,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,Let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:39.96,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Children are not allowed to watch people fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.02,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.50,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The event today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.11,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,will be a truly special occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:52.84,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,For this day, the King has granted us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.85,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,a priceless gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.19,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Two years ago, at the Great War at Marineford...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.79,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,a man lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:09.45,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,He was second commander of the legendary Whitebeard Pirates, and the son of the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.30,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:18.01,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,They say his fists of flame could pierce warships...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:22.19,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,or burn cities to the ground\Nand turn them into a living hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:30.17,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,This formidable power has returned to the world.\NReborn in the form of a new Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.92,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,R-Reborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.84,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.42,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:41.43,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,This forbidden fruit\Nwill be given to the victor of today's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:46.27,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,One of the Logia Devil Fruits,\Nthe strongest of the three varieties!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:52.60,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The Flame Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.20,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.80,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,The young master\Nwould never lie about something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.12,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Ace's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Flame Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:16.17,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Today our colosseum will be host to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:20.24,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,great men from all parts of the New World\Nwho have been summoned by our King.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:25.91,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,However!  This gem will not be handed over easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:33.48,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,If anyone thinks they can steal it,\NI'd like to see them try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.85,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,It is being guarded by people far more powerful\Nthan our usual combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.35,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Namely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.68,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,members of the esteemed Donquixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:49.48,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Senor Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.67,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.31,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Lao G!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.57,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Machvise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.99,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:11.35,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,And last but not least, the hero of our colosseum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:16.83,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Mr. Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.23,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Diamante-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.52,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Let's get this thing started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.50,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Let's see some blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:43.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What... is Ace's Flame Fruit doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:50.93,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Each devil fruit is unique\Nand no two have the same power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:55.19,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,But when a devil fruit user dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:11:01.11,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,the fruit that holds that power will reappear again somewhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:06.33,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,And whoever eats the new fruit\Nwill become the next holder of its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:11.35,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,After Fire Fist Ace died,\Nthe Flame Fruit reappeared somewhere unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.05,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,Until the young master managed to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:17.92,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,He's giving away a Logia devil fruit as a prize for his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.87,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,The young master is much more generous than he needs to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:25.10,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,I'm sure my life would be changed if I could gain that amazing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Like hell I'd let you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:32.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Ace was your...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I want that Flame Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!  Why don't you eat it, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.11,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'd rather not become an anchor. { def: dude, you're like 60% metal already.  how much swimming are you doing? }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:45.89,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I've already eaten the Rubber Fruit,\Nso I can't eat another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:50.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,but I don't want some random stranger to run off with Ace's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.30,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So it's like a memento for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:58.60,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Thinking of what Doflamingo said,\Nthis is probably a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.38,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,All I'll say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.75,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Don't let this chance slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.04,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You'd just end up regretting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.83,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Besides, we've got business at the colosseum anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.62,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.42,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,You fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.81,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,If wanting it was all it took,\Nnobody would lose their lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.73,Main,Masked man,0,0,0,,You underestimate the danger of the colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:30.29,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(300,0)}Mysterious Fairy Pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.83,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Fairy, my ass!  He's just some thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.20,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I keep telling you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.86,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Surely you can lose a sword.  Or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.85,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Like hell I can, you damned idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:48.85,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Dammit! Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.13,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.48,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Did you find the fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:12.39,Captions,,0,0,240,,{\fad(480,480)}Dancer\NViolet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.37,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Such sweetness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.61,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Such passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.85,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,No one in the world can match your dancing! {Xemnas: No one in the world can match the laziness of that animation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.05,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Sh-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.63,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,She's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:37.66,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten\Nthat women in this country stab men to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.33,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You're just gonna wind up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd gladly let her stab me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.31,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Shit!  I lost sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.48,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,That Moss-Head got himself lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.29,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Right, this is an excellent opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.51,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Let's just leave him here.\NHe's nothing but trouble anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.37,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I did everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:16.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Looks like this place is filled with couples.\NI'm really jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:27.29,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I wonder if this place would make\NNami-san and Robin-chan hopelessly fall for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.72,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Hello, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.32,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,You're the one who was looking at me earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.64,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.41,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,hold me in your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.33,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.25,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Where did she run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:56.70,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,She must have snuck out the back door into Lovers' Avenue.  She can't be far!{Good thing they aren't just doing a full 360 around on their immediate surroundings. I think they would probably have spotted her. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.24,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Don't let her get out of the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.28,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Yes sir! { def: does this count as translating?  cause if it does i think i could be a translator } {Xemnas: lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.94,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Thank you.  It looks like they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.59,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.69,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,you can let go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.06,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Oh, you are very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:22.99,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!  Did you hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:27.31,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No, the only thing that has hit me is the impact of our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.41,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,But there's so much blood!{Dear anime-creators everywhere. THAT IS NOT WHERE THE BLOOD GOES WHEN ONE IS TURNED ON. SRSLY. WHERE DID THAT STEREOTYPE EVEN COME FROM. -Starfish} {Xemnas: That's Japan for you. If you ever come across something weird, 99% of the time it originated in Japan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.48,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.68,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Poor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.28,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It's no use!  I cannot resist this passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.64,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.86,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,I have forsaken love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.92,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Every man I've gotten involved with{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.73,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:54.57,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,They were all in paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.37,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You were being chased, right?  Who were those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:01.81,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do to help, just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.08,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,That was the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.69,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,I... stabbed a man to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:15.29,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,because our love had turned sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.05,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:22.01,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You mean it's true?!  Women in this country really {\i1}are{\i0} passionate enough to kill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.95,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.74,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,You're okay with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.15,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:33.11,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,No, you can't just forgive a demonic woman like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.08,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Or I might...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.72,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.48,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,My name is Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:49.95,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind\Nas to escort me to the next town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.02,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,And once there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.63,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,will you kill a man for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:05.10,Captions,,0,0,210,,{\fad(420,0)}Corrida Colosseum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.10,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\an8}The colosseum is enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:09.24,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Just listen to those cheers!\NSuddenly, I wanna participate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,They're really getting fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.11,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,You've caused so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.00,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Just give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.78,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Criminal toy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.44,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,No good!  You can't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.47,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jet Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.80,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Look, my dear slugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.90,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have entered the colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:37.17,Captions,,0,0,240,,{\fad(500,0)}One-legged soldier\N Alternate Name: The Mad Thunder Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.41,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know the law, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.91,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Cops and marines\Nare forbidden to enter the colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:48.68,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Even if you see criminals within the colosseum, you have no authority here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:54.11,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,The only law that applies in here\Nis the law of the Donquixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:59.42,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Pull those triggers, and {\i1}you{\i0} will be the criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:01.73,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Now get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.67,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:11.60,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me old man!\NShall I carry your luggage for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.60,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What's this?  He sure got real polite all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What a funny soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.21,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,You find me funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.62,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,How about this?  How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.32,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Could you step aside, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.06,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Oh, am I in your way?  How terribly rude of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.94,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You're blushing like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.30,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You're really serious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.86,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:44.58,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,Making people smile is a toy's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.57,Main,Soldier-san,0,0,0,,As if there could ever be such a thing as a serious toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's taking it personally!{...I will admit, I am not sure I fully understand this conversation =/ -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:56.18,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,The open sign-up for today's battle\Nis about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.28,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,Not that any commoners\Nwould want to participate, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.09,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,They're too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:05.30,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy.  Looks like that's your entrance over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.73,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm participating!  Sign me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:12.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does that old man want to enter?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Is he nuts?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Does he have any idea what he's doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey Luffy, listen. Promise me just one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You can go all out if you want but don't ever let them know who you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sign your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Luf...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.95,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(450,0)}Fighter Number 556 - Lucy
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the dressing room for the competitors.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You're free until we call you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so exciting!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The Flame Fruit is mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's mine, idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's the little guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we use any weapons we like?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, who is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.61,0:20:39.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's the last participant to sign up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this shrimp doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:53.23,Captions,,0,0,240,,{\fad(450,0)}Spartan\NCorrida Colosseum Gladiator (51 Time Winner of the Monthly Tournament)
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the worst kind of joke!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.41,0:21:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, fake-bearded brat! This is a fighting arena!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't, Spartan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.11,0:21:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no fun seeing a weakling get pummeled!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The spectators only get excited when the strong go head-to-head!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,This is not a place for you! Go home!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Go home now!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya'!
